title: 90. The Tin Foil Show Ft. Tommy Vext
itunes:title: 90. The Tin Foil Show Ft. Tommy Vext
description: We've been programmed into believing things that are not reality. On today's episode, Andy and the crew talk with Tommy Vext from "Bad Wolves" about cancel culture, rejecting socialism and what the future looks like for America if we don't stand up for what we know is right.
